      "text": "貂蝉上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00026",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "听呼唤移步奔虎帐，十指尖尖捧茶汤。走向前，用目望，杀气森森貌堂堂。低头不语双膝跪，",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00027",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "貂蝉跪。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00028",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "慢睁凤眼看端详。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00029",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "下跪可是貂蝉？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00030",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00031",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "为何不抬起头来？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00032",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "有罪不敢抬头。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00033",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "恕你无罪。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00034",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "多谢二将军！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00035",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00036",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "灯光下见貂蝉十分美俊，好似那嫦蛾降下凡尘。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00037",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "貂蝉！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00038",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00039",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "你既是司徒王允之女，可知历代褒贬之事，",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00040",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "小女子不知。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00041",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "知道什么？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00042",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "知道三杰。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00043",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "哪三杰?",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00044",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "周三杰、汉三杰。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00045",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "何为“周三杰”？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00046",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "周公、太公、召公。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00047",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "“汉三杰”呢？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00048",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "张良、韩信、萧何。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00049",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "自周朝以来，古今出了多少名将？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00050",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "小女子才疏学浅，倘有差错，望二将军指教。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00051",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "你且讲来！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00052",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "二将军容禀！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00053",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "讲！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00054",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "前三皇后五帝道德为上，有尧舜和禹汤四大明王。周文王梦飞熊夜入虎帐，渭水河访贤臣定国安邦。十八国伍子胥盟辅上将，十二国钟无盐女中豪强。前七国有孙庞二人斗智，后七国有乐毅兵伐齐邦。前汉朝至平帝出了王莽，光武帝整乾坤迁都洛阳。小女子说不尽古今良将，一朝君一朝臣犬吠尧王。",
      "text_length": 132
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00055",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "有关某闻言心中高兴，好一个貂婵女与众不同。我不问前朝的兴和废，单问你虎牢关谁是英雄？",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00056",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "我闻言吃一惊心中暗想，口问心心问口自己思量：战沙场论英雄可算吕布，但是难比刘、关、张。走向前屈膝跪，尊一声二将军细听端详:论英雄三将军天下无双，",
      "text_length": 72
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00057",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "你丈夫吕布呢？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00058",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "那吕布三姓奴臭名远扬。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00059",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "你可曾见过我那三弟？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00060",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "虎牢关摆战场，金鼓声喧鬼神忙！",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00061",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "我那三弟他头戴？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00062",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "头戴着乌金盔盔缨灿亮，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00063",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "他身穿？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00064",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "身穿着乌油甲甲放毫光。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00065",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "胯下？",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00066",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "胯下一骑乌骓马，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00067",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "手使何物？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00068",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "手使一杆丈八枪。在阵前吼一声犹如雷响，好一似黑煞神下了天堂。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00069",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00070",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "好一个貂蝉女能言善讲，言来语去有文章。成全她名扬世间上，青锋剑斩她一命亡。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00071",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "关羽拔剑。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00072",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "貂蝉！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03080005_e00073",
      "play_id": "03080005",
      "scene_id": "03080005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
